list.abstract: .NET是 Microsoft XML Web services 平台。XML Web services 允许应用程序通过 Internet 进行通讯和共享数据，而不管所采用的是哪种操作系统、设备或编程语言。Microsoft .NET 平台提供创建 XML Web services 并将这些服务集成在一起之所需。对个人用户的好处是无缝的、吸引人的体验。

yingyinNormal.en: It's called ornithophobia. And someday it will be recognized as a true disability, and the landlord will be required by law to put a giant net over the building. Which is unfortunate, because I have a fear of nets.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这叫恐鸟症。而且总有一天，恐鸟症会被视为一种残疾，房东必须按照法律规定给这栋楼加一张大网，到时就悲剧了，因为我还怕网。

yingyinNormal.en: Every form he's built, every trace of his presence on the net. We have to act now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他制造的机器，他在网络上的一切痕迹，我们必须马上行动。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm the proud owner of wilwheatonstinks.com, .net, and .org. What does that tell you?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我可是“臭威尔惠顿”企业网站，互联网站和机构网站的所有人，知道这说明什么吗？

yingyinNormal.en: If a player scores a goal, it ultimately has a stronger impact on your impression of their skills than if they miss the net.
yingyinNormal.zh: 足球员射门得分，这最后会有个更强的影响加深你对他们球技的印象，比起他们没有得分的话。

yingyinNormal.en: But I also want you to kick in a $250,000 credit line with 10% interest to be paid back in full once we meet net revenue positive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 并且我给你最多250000美元的投资限额投资回报率为10%从我们净收入为正的时候开始算。

examination_example.sentence: The Republican-penned order eliminated the strict <highlight>net</highlight> neutrality rules the FCC had adopted when it had a Democratic majority in 2015.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 共和党起草的这项命令取消了FCC在2015年民主党占多数时采用的严格的网络中立规则。

examination_example.sentence: In the meantime, the court threw out the FCC's attempt to block all state rules on <highlight>net</highlight> neutrality.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 与此同时，法院驳回了联邦通信委员会阻止所有关于网络中立的州规则的企图。

examination_example.sentence: That means more battles like the one now going on between the Justice Department and California, which enacted a tough <highlight>net</highlight> neutrality law.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这意味着会有更多类似司法部和加利福尼亚州之间的斗争，后者制定了严格的网络中立法。

word_usage.usage: net表示“网”或“网状物”时不可数，而在指“渔网”等有某种用途的网时，为可数名词。
net作形容词，表示“净得的; 纯的”时，必须放在名词前，如：net income 纯收入。
